草根场地 Matchstick Piehouse 在与房东的斗争中失败，宣布计划成为工人合作社https://www.nme.com/news/music/grassroots-venue-matchstick-piehouse-loses-battle-with-landlord-plans-workers-coop-3565672?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=grassroots-venue-matchstick-馅饼屋输掉了与房东计划工人合作社的战斗Liberty DunworthThu, 04 Jan 2024 16:12:22 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3565672 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="观看音乐表演的人群 图库照片" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>房东威胁终止租约后发起了一场运动</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grassroots-venue-matchstick-piehouse-loses-battle-with-landlord-plans-workers-coop-3565672">草根场地 Matchstick Piehouse 在与房东的斗争中失败，宣布计划成为工人合作社，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="观看音乐表演的人群 图库照片" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Music-Venue@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦东南部的场馆 Matchstick Piehouse 宣布，它在与房东的斗争中输掉了继续营业的斗争，并透露计划改建为工人合作社。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-to-lose-10-per-cent-of-grassroots-venues-in-2023-as-calls-grow-for-rest-of-industry-to-invest-3499727">随着要求其他行业投资的呼声越来越高，英国将在 2023 年失去 10% 的基层场馆</a></strong></li></ul><p>去年 11 月，这个位于德特福德铁路拱门的草根场馆的未来受到质疑，当时该场馆的工作人员呼吁其支持者为筹款活动捐款以保持开放。</p><p>在此之前，该场馆的房东“威胁要终止租约”，除非他们能够在本周末筹集到 35,000 英镑。由于大流行限制后贸易下降，该地点（一个酒吧、音乐场所和艺术空间）承受了压力。</p><p> “我们花了所有的时间[……]试图找到一个解决方案，让我们能够敞开大门，”该场馆 Instagram 页面上的最初帖子写道。 “不幸的是，我们花了几天时间才得到房东的回复；当他们联系上时，他们说我们需要在 11 月 29 日之前支付 36,000 英镑才能继续租约。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0HKQ-do4MR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke