sic/green-day-release-new-single-dilemma-listen-watch-video-3555305">“困境”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elon-musk-mocks-green-day-for-changing-lyrics-to-american-idiot-during-new-years-eve-performance-3565665">埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 嘲笑绿日乐队 (Green Day) 在除夕表演期间更改了《美国白痴》(American Idiot) 的歌词，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
