e-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两人结婚七年后于上个月分手</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-responds-to-rumours-that-she-and-offset-are-back-together-3565646">Cardi B 回应有关她和 Offset“复合”的谣言的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="卡迪B" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Offset-and-Cardi-B-attend-the-2023-MTV-Video-Music-Awards-at-Prudential-Center-on-September-12-2023-in-Newark-New-Jersey.-Photo-by-Catherine-PowellGetty-Images-for-MTV-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a>回应了她和丈夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/offset">Offset</a>复合的传闻。</p><p>这对说唱歌手夫妇自 2017 年 9 月起就结婚了，尽管他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-confirms-married-offset-last-year-2343857">直到 2018 年 6 月才确认结婚</a>。他们有两个孩子： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-offsets-child-born-raising-middle-finger-2366245">Kulture Kiari Cephus Almanzar</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-and-offset-announce-birth-of-their-second-child-3038648">Wave Set Cephus Almanzar</a> 。</p><p>在他们结婚初期，有报道称 Offset 涉嫌对 Cardi 不忠，导致两人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-announces-separation-migos-offset-2416731">于 2018 年 12 月分居</a>。 “我现在一直在努力和我的小父亲解决问题，”Cardi B 当时解释道。 “我们彼此非常相爱，但我们之间的事情已经很长时间没有进展了，这不是任何人的错。”</p><p>卡迪随后于 2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-has-reportedly-filed-for-divorce-from-offset-2753729">提出离婚</a>，声称“没有和解的希望”。然而，一个月后，这位“WAP”说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-says-she-has-decided-not-to-divorce-offset-2786261">决定不再这样做</a>：“我离婚的原因并不是因为以前没有发生过这种事。不是因为作弊。我看到人们会说，‘哦，他的孩子就要出生了。’这完全是一个彻头彻尾的谎言。这是人们第二次试图将婴儿钉在这里。不，那是胡说八道。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/offset-denies-cheating-on-cardi-b-with-rapper-chrisean-rock-3557246">上个月，Offset 否认了卡迪与说唱歌手克里安·洛克 (Chrisean Rock) 不忠的传闻</a>，并宣布两人最新分手，卡迪现在证实，尽管一起度过了新年前夜，但两人并没有“复合”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3503723" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3503723" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3503723" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV.jpg" alt="Offset 和 Cardi B" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/offset-cardi-b-getty-Catherine-Powell_Getty-Images-for-MTV-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3503723" class="wp-caption-text"> Offset 和 Cardi B 亮相 2023 年 VMA。图片来源：Catherine Powell/MTV 盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>卡迪在 X/Twitter 上的 Spaces 直播中表示：“我想向你们澄清，因为你们正在做出自己的假设，我只是想让你们从马口中听到它。</p><p> “我昨天是在和我的小爸爸去泡吧吗？是的。我昨天是不是被坑惨了？绝对是的，宝贝。”</p><p>她补充道：“我们都在同一个俱乐部，这真的很尴尬。就像，我在我的区域，他在他的区域。所以这就像是，‘伙计，他妈的过来吧。让我们冷静一下。我们玩得很开心。</p><p> “复合的答案不是在俱乐部度过一个美好的夜晚，然后彻夜狂欢，”卡迪继续说道。 “我们需要在我们的事情上努力，我们需要在我们的沟通上努力，有些事情他需要努力，有些事情我需要努力。”</p><p> “这是一个有趣的夜晚，然后你猜怎么着，第二天我们会争论，第二天我会阻止。接下来你知道，我们已经四天没有说话了。我不想让这个循环继续下去。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-responds-to-rumours-that-she-and-offset-are-back-together-3565646">Cardi B 回应有关她和 Offset“复合”的谣言的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
